Please download GoldenDictPortable version from following link
http://sourceforge.net/projects/portableapps/files/GoldenDict%20Portable/GoldenDictPortable_1.0.1.paf.exe/download

then please follow the steps below:
1. Install the file  GoldenDictPortable_1.0.1.paf.exe downloaded by providing portable device address.  
   Once done, GoldenDictPortable folder is created
2. Open GoldenDictPortable.exe file inside above folder
3. unzip all the dictionaries inside
      GoldenDictPortable/App/GoldenDict/content/
4. In GoldenDict go to Edit->Dictionaries
5. Click on Rescan now
6. Click OK
